Get crazy with the … BeautifulSoup 

Looping lists in Python and R Third in our series, we dive straight into web-scraping. (‘Bout time!) 

Syntax Handling loops and lists in Python and R have very similar syntax, if we stick to the standard for-loop.

It’s when we get to R’s lapply from the apply family of functions and Python’s list compression that we see some real divergence. Both can be a bit of a mind-job the first time you see it.